---
layout: default
title: Newsletter
description: Subscribe to my newsletter
---

<div class="container">
  <section class="newsletter-intro">
    <h1>Newsletter</h1>
    <p class="text-xl mb-8">
      I send a newsletter about product design and leadership, with a touch of email and climate tech, once or twice a month.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section class="newsletter-signup">
    <iframe src="https://embeds.beehiiv.com/71d951d8-d80b-4908-b7c3-7b5ec6fb54e7?slim=true" data-test-id="beehiiv-embed" height="52" frameborder="0" scrolling="no" style="margin: 0; border-radius: 0px !important; background-color: transparent;"></iframe>
    <p>If you subscribe, I promise I’ll never share or sell your info, or track you in a creepy way. You’ll always be able to unsubscribe anytime instantly.</p>
    
    <h2>Past issues</h2>
    {% if newsletter.issues and newsletter.issues.length > 0 %}
      <ul>
        {% for issue in newsletter.issues %}
          <li>
            <a href="{{ issue.url }}" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
              {{ issue.title }} - {{ issue.date }}
            </a>
          </li>
        {% endfor %}
      </ul>
    {% else %}
      <p>Loading past issues...</p>
    {% endif %}
  </section>
</div>